items.title: Syria says operation against Assad loyalists over after deadly violence
items.description: A monitoring group says 973 civilians have been killed in revenge attacks against the Alawite sect since Thursday.

items.title: Stocks slide as Trump warns of US economy 'transition'
items.description: New retaliatory tariffs from China targeting some US farm products came into effect on Monday.

items.title: US expects 'substantial progress' in peace talks with Ukraine
items.description: Ukraine is under US pressure to accept a quick truce to end the war with Russia, with US-Ukrainian talks set to begin in Saudi Arabia.

items.title: 'There's never been a spotlight like this': Greenland heads to the polls as Trump eyes territory
items.description: Donald Trump's vow to take over Greenland has shone a global spotlight on the island's elections.

items.title: Musk's Tesla facilities in US face 'Takedown' protests
items.description: It is part of an effort to protest the role Tesla's billionaire owner, Elon Musk, has played in the Trump administration.
